{"id": "574", "instruction": "Let $x_1, . . . ,x_{2024}$ be complex numbers such that for all $1 \\le i \\le 2024$\n$$$\\sum_{1\\le j_1<j_2<···<j_i\\le 2024} x_{j1}x_{j2}... x_{ji} = 1$$$\nCalculate $\\left|\\sum^{2024}_{i=1} x^{2024}_i \\right|$ .\n.\n\nOptions:\nA. 2024^2\nB. 2023\nC. 2024\nD. 2024 - 3\nE. 2024 - 2\nF. 1\nG. 2022\nH. 2024 + 1\nI. 2025\nJ. 2024 - 1", "output": "F"}
